        "title": "Add official publisher badges",
        "body": "Summary\n- Derive Official publisher state from the hard-coded `openclaw` org: the `openclaw` org publisher is Official, and current `openclaw` org members' personal publishers are Official while membership exists.\n- Remove the generic publisher-official endpoint path; arbitrary publishers are not marked Official through API/admin mutation.\n- Sync derived Official state to public skill/package badges, package channel/isOfficial fields, search digests, and publisher/profile UI.\n- Expose Official state through public API schemas and render the blue Official badge in publisher, skill, and plugin views.\n- Document that `trustedPublisher` is separate from Official and does not make a publisher/package Official.\n\nVerification\n- `bun run test src/__tests__/packages-route.test.tsx`\n- `bun run test`\n- `bun run test convex/publishers.test.ts convex/packages.public.test.ts convex/skills.packageCatalog.test.ts convex/skills.ownership.test.ts convex/skills.ownerMigration.test.ts convex/skills.reclaim.test.ts convex/maintenance.test.ts`\n- `bun run test src/components/SkillHeader.test.tsx src/components/PublisherListItem.test.tsx src/components/PluginListItem.test.tsx src/components/SkillListItem.test.tsx src/components/UserBadge.test.tsx src/components/PublishedItemCard.test.tsx src/__tests__/packages-route.test.tsx src/__tests__/package-detail-route.test.tsx`\n- `bun run --cwd packages/clawhub test:src src/cli/commands/skills.test.ts src/skills.test.ts`\n- `bun run format:check`\n- `bun run lint`\n- `VITE_CONVEX_URL=https://example.invalid bunx tsc --noEmit`\n- `bunx tsc -p packages/schema/tsconfig.json --noEmit`\n- `bunx tsc -p packages/clawhub/tsconfig.json --noEmit`\n- `bunx vitest run -c vitest.e2e.config.ts e2e/permissions.e2e.test.ts`\n",
